ContentDesc_Götterdämmerung - Ifrit: While your victory over the Ultima Weapon has set off waves of celebration across the land, the jubilation is short-lived, for the beast tribes are seeking to summon their gods once more. Confirmation has arrived that the Amalj'aa have already succeeded in calling forth Ifrit, who is returned far mightier than his last incarnation owing to the vast amounts of crystals he has gorged upon. Prepare yourself for a scorching encounter.
QuestName_Ifrit Bleeds, We Can Kill It: Ifrit Bleeds, We Can Kill It
